      "rationale": "Reynolds-Averaged Navier-Stokes with SST k-ω turbulence closure selected based on published literature for rotating blood pump CFD. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) applied with published constants. Turbulence model sensitivity study (SST k-ω vs. realizable k-ε) shows NHI spread < 6.2%, confirming model-form robustness."
